# Regenerable build artifacts from tools/mesen-labels.py --asm (project the toml
# onto the native disasm). Deterministic from mesen-labels.toml + source/1-asm-6502/bank_NN.asm,
# so we don't version them. Regenerate: py -3 -m mesen-labels --asm (from tools/)
source/1-asm-6502/*_named.asm

# Rendered tactical fief maps — regenerable from ROM via tools/batch-render-fief-maps.py
# (the decoded map_populate + CHR + palette path). High byte-count, deterministic,
# repeatable, so we don't version them. Regenerate: py batch-render-fief-maps.py
assets/maps/fiefs/17/
assets/maps/fiefs/50/
assets/maps/fiefs/*.png
